{{Quote|It's something called the Eternity Crystal&hellip; We're not exactly sure how it works&hellip; But apparently it was the pinnacle of Jerni science.|Luke Skywalker|<ref name="Dark Knight's Devilry">{{StoryCite|story=Dark Knight's Devilry|book=The Empire Strikes Back Monthly 153}}</ref>}}
The '''Eternity Crystal''' was allegedly the pinnacle of [[Jerni]] science, capable of [[Time travel/Legends|winding back time]] from a horrendous event, and guiding the future (present) in a different and more positive direction.

The crystal was supposedly hidden in the Jerni ruins near [[Adony Station]], but it turned out the whole thing was a hoax devised by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] in an [[Mission to Jerne|attempt]] to kill [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]].

